body_html: @w9wang2 Do you have your build.gradle set up to grab an explicit version of the TF library? This should be fixed in 1.3.1-alpha. It looks like you're grabbing a 1.3.0 release, which did not build in the necessary bool support.

body: @w9wang2 Do you have your build.gradle set up to grab an explicit version of the TF library? This should be fixed in [1.3.1-alpha](https://bintray.com/google/tensorflow/tensorflow/1.3.1-alpha). It looks like you're grabbing a 1.3.0 release, which did not build in the necessary bool support.
